Amazon S3 Component for CakePHP 2.x

fork from https://github.com/mikedube-/cakephp2-amazon-s3

Installation

1. copy S3Component.php to your components folder

2. define settings:
    copy config.php to Config folder and add to bootstrap.php this row:
		
		Configure::load('config');

	or just set variables in core.php as 
	
		Configure::write('Amazon.key', 'KEY');
	
all roes from config.php"

3. get last code from http://undesigned.org.za/2007/10/22/amazon-s3-php-class and put S3.php to Vendor folder


Implementation

	public $components = array('S3'); in your controller
